1. U *snovima* sam imao divan san. (In my *dreams* I had a wonderful dream.)
2. Oni su se nadali da će njihovi *snovi* postati stvarnost. (They hoped that their *dreams* would become reality.)
3. Sreća je nešto što svi želimo u svojim *snovima*. (Happiness is something we all want in our *dreams*.)
4. Nikada ne gubiš nadu ako veruješ u svoje *snove*. (You never lose hope if you believe in your *dreams*.)
5. Zgrada se nalazi u *snovima* ljudi koji sanjaju o uspehu. (The building is located in the *dreams* of people who dream of success.)
6. Moji *snovi* su se ostvarili kada sam upoznao svoju ljubav. (My *dreams* came true when I met my love.)
7. Nije dovoljno samo sanjati *snove*, moraš raditi na njihovoj realizaciji. (It's not enough just to dream *dreams*, you have to work on their realization.)
8. Sve što smo u stanju da zamislimo, može postati stvarnost u našim *snovima*. (Everything we can imagine can become a reality in our *dreams*.)